 conky.text = [[
Launch Terminal$alignr Super+Enter
Launch Browser$alignr Super+Shift+Enter
Launch Application$alignr Super+Space
Choose Window$alignr Super+Ctrl+Space

Go to Workspace 1$alignr Super+1
Go to Workspace n$alignr Super+n
Next Workspace$alignr Super+Tab
Last Workspace$alignr Super+Shift+Tab

Toggle Layout Mode$alignr Super+Backspace

Resize Window Mode$alignr Super+r
Exit Resize Window Mode$alignr Escape
Focused Window Fullscreen Toggle$alignr Super+f
Floating Window Mode Toggle$alignr Super+Shift+f
Kill Active Window$alignr Super+Shift+q

Move Window to WS 1$alignr Super+Shift+1
Move Window to WS n$alignr Super+Shift+n

Change Window Focus$alignr Super+[↑]/[↓]/[←]/[→]
$alignr Super+[k]/[j]/[h]/[l]
Move Window$alignr Super+Shift+[↑]/[↓]/[←]/[→]
$alignr Super+Shift+[k]/[j]/[h]/[l]

Resize Window Gaps$alignr Super+[+]/[-]

Control Center$alignr Super+c

Lock Screen$alignr Super+Escape
Sleep$alignr Super+Shift+s
Logout$alignr Super+Shift+e

Toggle This Window$alignr Super+Shift+?]]